chemo_detail:

from 02.04.2018 up to 27.09.2018>
Now on Single agent Gemcitabine 1600mg D1&8 q3w started from 19.11.2022, (C2D8 received 2000 as
dose increased from 1000mg/m2 to 1250mmg/m2). C6D8 completed on 4.03.2023 with increased dose
of 2gm
